octavia_load_balancer_logs_main_descript: Below are the logs for your load balancer, separated into categories such as TCP, HTTP, HTTPS, and TERMINATED_HTTPS (please note that UDP is not supported). These logs are those generated by the HAProxy OpenSource component.
